Enjoying the last bits of Fall in New England 🍁 #fall #newengland #newhampshire #travel

Wrapping up one of the best years yet! 2023 was one filled with love, new friendships, and lots of travel. Overall thankful for everything and everyone in my life and, in 2024, I aim to share more moments on here. This year I have taken breaks from instagram to focus on being present, but I hope to find a balance this year and continue the reason I started posting on instagram in the first place, for the connection with others. Here's to another year of growth and hope everyone has a wonderful new year! #2023 #travel
